spirit:component.spirit:name: PmodHYGRO_axi_timer_0_0
spirit:component.spirit:description: The AXI Timer/Counter is a 32/64-bit timer module that attaches to the AXI4-Lite interface

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: TRIG0_ASSERT
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Assertion level for capture trigger0. It can be active high or active low

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: TRIG1_ASSERT
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Assertion level for capture trigger1. It can be active high or active low

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: GEN0_ASSERT
spirit:parameter.spirit:displayName: Active state of Generate Out signal
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Assertion level for generateout0. It can be active high or active low

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: GEN1_ASSERT
spirit:parameter.spirit:displayName: Active state of Generate Out signal
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Assertion level for generateout1. It can be active high or active low

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: COUNT_WIDTH
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Width of timer can be selected from the range of 8 to 32

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: mode_64bit
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: This is cascaded mode. The two timer are cascaded to operate as a single 64 bit counter
